==English==
===Verb===
'''to respire'''

#(''intransitive'') To breathe in and out
#(''intransitive'') To engage in the process of [[respiration]]
#(''intransitive'') To recover one's breath or breathe easily following stress
#(''transitive'') To inhale and exhale); to breathe

